Get DisMAP layer names, given region season

Source: R/dismapr.R
get_dm_dataset_layers.Rd

Get a list of available layers for a given region and season

Usage

get_dm_dataset_layers(dataset_code)

Arguments

datset_code

The region (and season) code, per available dataset_code in dm_regions

Value

A character vector of layer names, usually species scientific name or "Species Richness"

Examples

get_dm_dataset_layers("AI")
